# Ultimate BLT

Based on [https://www.cookwell.com/recipe/...](https://www.cookwell.com/recipe/blt) and [https://fieldcompany.com/blogs/...](https://fieldcompany.com/blogs/journal/how-to-cook-bacon-in-a-cast-iron-skillet)

